OL,6,FA Dorset tea company is celebrating
OL,7,Fits 40th birthday and 30 years of fair
OL,8,Ftrading.
OL,10,FClipper Tea, based in Beaminster, is
OL,11,Fnow just a few miles from the house
OL,12,Fwhere the business was started in 1984.
OL,14,FThey wanted to share their love of
OL,15,Fgreat tea with a promise of ethical
OL,16,Fsourcing and natural production.
OL,18,FIt was founded by husband and wife,
OL,19,FMike and Lorraine Brehme in their
OL,20,Fkitchen.
