OL,6,FThe company gradually grew, leading to
OL,7,Fit being sold in the 2000s.
OL,9,FToday, the business still produces tea
OL,10,Fat its factory in Beaminster and
OL,11,Fretains an ethos of fair trade, having
OL,12,Fbeen involved with the Fairtrade
OL,13,FFoundation for 30 years.
OL,15,FThe company now has over 150 different
OL,16,FClipper products, sold in over 50
OL,17,Fcountries.
