OL,6,FIn 1994 the company became the UK's
OL,7,Ffirst Fairtrade tea company and is now
OL,8,Fthe world's largest buyer of Fairtrade
OL,9,Ftea, supporting over 114,000 producers
OL,10,Fand their families around the globe.
OL,12,FHayley Murgett, global head of
OL,13,Fmarketing at Clipper, said: "Since
OL,14,Fwe've been in partnership with them
OL,15,Fwe've helped to raise over #6.8
OL,16,Fmillion to go towards fair trade
OL,17,Fprojects and help local communities
OL,18,Freally grow and establish vital
OL,19,Fhealthcare, building schools and even
OL,20,Fprovide an ambulance at one particular
OL,21,Ftea plantation."
