OL,7,Fcampaigns manager at the Fairtrade
OL,8,FFoundation, said: "This year we're
OL,9,Fcelebrating 30 years of fair trade and
OL,10,Fwe're urging everyone to 'be the
OL,11,Fchange'.
OL,13,F"By buying Fairtrade we can ensure
OL,14,Fthat farmers and workers across the
OL,15,Fworld can build stronger and more
OL,16,Fresilient communities."
